  <img src="../images/v/vxt-d2051b.gif" alt="[triarched triangular shield example]" border="0" height="108"></a><br />
  <em>Arms and flag of <a href="ba-04-te.html">Te�anj</a>, Bosnia and Herzegovina (fotw)</em></dl>

